86, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1314, \"end\": 1327, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Law_enforcement_in_France\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.7959078928592628e-26, \"text\": \"French police\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Law_enforcement_in_France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Law_enforcement_in_France\"}, {\"begin\": 1363, \"end\": 1368, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999879492, \"rank\": 1.1967801383341149e-11, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Paris City Hall officials said that no policing plans for the upcoming Olympic Games were lost in the theft of computer gear reported by one of its employees.\", \"from\": 1387, \"to\": 1545, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"(AP Photo/Thibault Camus, File)  In a city repeatedly hit by deadly extremist attacks, security is the biggest challenge for Paris Games organizers.\", \"from\": 1545, \"to\": 1693, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1670, \"end\": 1675, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999879492, \"rank\": 1.1967801383341149e-11, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Paris prosecutor's office on Wednesday described media coverage of the theft as \\\"hasty.\\\"\", \"from\": 1695, \"to\": 1787, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1699, \"end\": 1704, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999879492, \"rank\": 1.1967801383341149e-11, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It said a City Hall engineer had lost a bag at Gare du Nord on Monday and reported that it contained a USB key used for work.\", \"from\": 1788, \"to\": 1913, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1891, \"end\": 1894, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USB_flash_drive\", \"score\": 0.9728723472723383, \"rank\": 0.02788408108538198, \"text\": \"USB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USB_flash_drive\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USB_flash_drive\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"MEDALS FOR THE 2024 PARIS OLYMPICS ARE MADE FROM EIFFEL TOWER PIECES  \\\"However, it is important to specify that this key only contained notes related to traffic in Paris during the Olympic Games, and not on sensitive security plans,\\\" the prosecutor's office said.\", \"from\": 1915, \"to\": 2178, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2079, \"end\": 2084, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999879492, \"rank\": 1.1967801383341149e-11, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"City Hall's statement said the worker's computer gear \\\"contained notes for internal use,\\\" concerning the employee's IT-related work forthe Paristraffic department.\", \"from\": 2180, \"to\": 2343, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It said an investigation is underway into the \\\"proven breaches of internal security procedures\\\" and that depending on its findings, \\\"sanctions will be taken.\\\"\", \"from\": 2345, \"to\": 2503, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Fox News' Antisemitism Exposed\\\" newsletter brings you stories on the rising anti-Jewish prejudice across the U.S. and the world.\\\"\", \"from\": 2505, \"to\": 2634, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2505, \"end\": 2513, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fox_News\", \"score\": 0.999998753254526, \"rank\": 1.2467094002955614e-06, \"text\": \"Fox News\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fox_News\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org